<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="least-adv">least <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /liːst/    美 /liːst/  </p>
<p>[little的最高级]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>最少地；最小地</strong></h4>
<p>反 most </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>That was <strong>the least</strong> interesting story I'd ever read.
那是我读过的最无聊的书。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Happiness doesn't always come from a pursuit. Sometimes it comes when we least expect it.
幸福并不总是追求来的。它有时在我们最意料不到的时候来临。</p></div></div>